        "title": "Bump com.github.oshi:oshi-core from 6.8.1 to 6.8.2",
        "body": "Bumps [com.github.oshi:oshi-core](https://github.com/oshi/oshi) from 6.8.1 to 6.8.2.\n<details>\n<summary>Release notes</summary>\n<p><em>Sourced from <a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/releases\">com.github.oshi:oshi-core's releases</a>.</em></p>\n<blockquote>\n<h2>Release 6.8.2</h2>\n<h5>Bug fixes / Improvements</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/oshi/oshi/pull/2889\">#2889</a>: Handle system date format on macOS getInstalledApps output parsing - <a href=\"https://github.com/dyorgio\"><code>@​dyorgio</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md\">Full change log</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Changelog</summary>\n<p><em>Sourced from <a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md\">com.github.oshi:oshi-core's changelog</a>.</em></p>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Commits</summary>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/commit/e6842910093729e7d0e19bed13476383fa8d1062\"><code>e684291</code></a> [maven-release-plugin] prepare release oshi-parent-6.8.2</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/commit/57ac15f17765df975e6edfbdbe7745212d75cfca\"><code>57ac15f</code></a> 6.8.2 Release</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/commit/17bd549735c985a75c200516316a862c7ffe74cb\"><code>17bd549</code></a> chore(deps): update dependency org.junit.jupiter:junit-jupiter-api to v5.13.0...</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/commit/c9424a0c3c3413587899f904b4543c5a1851f0ef\"><code>c9424a0</code></a> Handle locale-specific formats on macOS system_profiler output (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/oshi/oshi/issues/2890\">#2890</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/commit/134ee60e0453594d6715f26f420455aab7cca1ff\"><code>134ee60</code></a> chore(deps): update dependency com.diffplug.spotless:spotless-maven-plugin to...</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/commit/f802bc6e187fbc13c93c6b93d6fe9e3b0d63aaad\"><code>f802bc6</code></a> add missing = to a key-value pair (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/oshi/oshi/issues/2893\">#2893</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/commit/a8546ee71506af1e5dafb9504ed7f23a3e078dee\"><code>a8546ee</code></a> chore(deps): update dependency io.github.git-commit-id:git-commit-id-maven-pl...</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/commit/ac8ca78b4372468bbc86d11da4e15a71fed2a2ed\"><code>ac8ca78</code></a> fix(deps): update dependency org.jfree:jfreechart to v1.5.6 (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/oshi/oshi/issues/2888\">#2888</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/commit/5637d5e0f0f90a37836d0afd4fa71d28e8814df5\"><code>5637d5e</code></a> chore(deps): update dependency com.puppycrawl.tools:checkstyle to v10.24.0 (#...</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/commit/39a20d2d82245a9dd325395537ea24f94ed7d2be\"><code>39a20d2</code></a> chore(deps): update dependency com.puppycrawl.tools:checkstyle to v10.23.1 (#...</li>\n<li>Additional commits viewable in <a href=\"https://github.com/oshi/oshi/compare/oshi-parent-6.8.1...oshi-parent-6.8.2\">compare view</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<br />\n\n\n[![user-1 compatibility score](https://user-1-badges.githubapp.com/badges/compatibility_score?dependency-name=com.github.oshi:oshi-core&package-manager=gradle&previous-version=6.8.1&new-version=6.8.2)](https://docs.github.com/en/github/managing-security-vulnerabilities/about-user-1-security-updates#about-compatibility-scores)\n\nuser-1 will resolve any conflicts with this PR as long as you don't alter it yourself. You can also trigger a rebase manually by commenting `@user-1 rebase`.\n\n[//]: # (user-1-automerge-start)\n[//]: # (user-1-automerge-end)\n\n---\n\n<details>\n<summary>user-1 commands and options</summary>\n<br />\n\nYou can trigger user-1 actions by commenting on this PR:\n- `@user-1 rebase` will rebase this PR\n- `@user-1 recreate` will recreate this PR, overwriting any edits that have been made to it\n- `@user-1 merge` will merge this PR after your CI passes on it\n- `@user-1 squash and merge` will squash and merge this PR after your CI passes on it\n- `@user-1 cancel merge` will cancel a previously requested merge and block automerging\n- `@user-1 reopen` will reopen this PR if it is closed\n- `@user-1 close` will close this PR and stop user-1 recreating it. You can achieve the same result by closing it manually\n- `@user-1 show <dependency name> ignore conditions` will show all of the ignore conditions of the specified dependency\n- `@user-1 ignore this major version` will close this PR and stop user-1 creating any more for this major version (unless you reopen the PR or upgrade to it yourself)\n- `@user-1 ignore this minor version` will close this PR and stop user-1 creating any more for this minor version (unless you reopen the PR or upgrade to it yourself)\n- `@user-1 ignore this dependency` will close this PR and stop user-1 creating any more for this dependency (unless you reopen the PR or upgrade to it yourself)\n\n\n</details>",
